{"tid":84154,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【嫌「亞視味」濃】憶起陳鴻烈拍劇猝逝 歐錦棠叫樂易玲做「婆娘」","createTime":"2017-01-17T10:29:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-17T17:17:22.000Z","uid":49391,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a31a99308d06dc9862ca3cd4e631884a69486f3f","tid":84154,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:29:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170117/large/1484646342_8b09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170117%2Flarge%2F1484646342_8b09.jpg&h=abdec88b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐錦棠接受周刊專訪，不避嫌咁叫樂小姐做「婆娘」。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n剛完成舞台劇《科學怪人》演出嘅歐錦棠，今日就有周刊嘅專訪中，憶起陳鴻烈當年拍大台劇時猝逝一事，歐錦棠不屑咁鬧爆一個人係「婆娘」。<br />\n<br />\n歐錦棠口中嘅「婆娘」，就係人稱「樂小姐」樂易玲。棠哥喺專訪入面講到2001年佢加入無綫，當時已備受重用，一劇接一劇，人氣都算唔錯，點知2003年樂小姐入咗無綫後，歐錦棠就冇運行。<br />\n專訪係咁講嘅，樂小姐入咗大台後，就即時召見棠哥，並唔係話要力捧佢，係叫佢忍吓喎！棠哥當時都好愕然，唔知樂小姐叫佢忍乜，之後就話佢有陣「亞視味」好重！<br />\n棠哥最嬲樂小姐嘅一件事，係當年陳鴻烈喺拍劇期間猝逝一事。2009年，佢同「大閆生」陳鴻烈拍攝《畢打自己人》時，陳鴻烈突然心臟病發，當時佢睇住陳鴻烈離世，佢同一班演員準備離醫院時，樂小姐同佢哋講，叫佢哋唔准話烈哥走咗，棠哥覺得佢唔准佢哋講嘅原因就係要等佢做發言人，但當時棠哥冇理佢，離開時就同記者講烈哥已經離開。<br />\n翻查當年報道，棠哥真係喺離開醫院時，喊住同記者講：「走咗喇，走咗喇！」(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iwumMy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iwumMy&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=e3f3f1ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iwumMy</a> )佢又重提樂小姐當時好似做咗「發言人」咁向記者交待烈哥離世嘅消息。其間佢仲講到歐錦棠扶烈哥去休息，有人俾一杯水烈哥飲(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2iBPbBq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2iBPbBq&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=2ab6b765\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2iBPbBq</a> )。但棠哥喺專訪中就否認有攞水俾烈哥飲，佢仲嬲到話可以睇翻當時閉路電視，話有人作嘢喎！佢又話今次用「婆娘」嚟形容樂小姐，一啲都唔驚，笑指驚佢有牙呀! <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170117/56184560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170117%2F56184560&d=TCv67g58sYfcFSVn91Z9VQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=d592755f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170117%2F56184560&h=df1246c1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170117/56184560</a>"},{"pid":"e1399af31d7474f9e6bd1c49679ead8bb4b72592","tid":84154,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"佢而家好似好大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0f2c6e6bf239abe4851980651db72149158768","tid":84154,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"男人老狗做埋d八婆野"},{"pid":"7239442ddc504182ec4cbc14f1a88a2e1931442d","tid":84154,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗做埋d八婆野</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係咪精神有問題?"},{"pid":"36bc48496fbe7a28b8e08cc7f2147bc9cf3aedef","tid":84154,"uid":69184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:44:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人老狗做埋d八婆野</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403cd042b5bc26383e052351d692efb984b436f7","tid":84154,"uid":8157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:44:26.000Z","msg":"唔洗你講都知佢係西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e72c343604db3c51403d712f73b9b34dfc8c7e9","tid":84154,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔洗你講都知佢係西女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411e8a050243bf683ab17a4ffef04dfd49996b98","tid":84154,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"條死八婆呢排失勢，班比佢地兩個女人趕走嘅猛人仲唔出返嚟屌到佢地反皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" c